lead_paragraph: The Indian spinners did succeed in bringing Kane Williamson and Tom Latham to their knees but only literally as the New Zealanders swept them to distraction on day two of the first test in Kanpur on Friday.

headline.print_headline: New Zealand Go Down on Their Knees to Combat Indian Spin
